sudo passwd wc(Ubuntu username)(~/home/wc) #to change password
After reboot, old password must be typed as final time.


cat /etc/lsb-release (to find current OS version)
top (show CPU Usage, Memory Usage, Process)  'q' to quit
lscpu (CPU detail info)


ifconfig
ping google.com
poweroff	reboot

